" or click the vertical ellipsis button (:guilabel:`⋮`) on a POS card and "
"click :guilabel:`Edit`. Then, enable :guilabel:`Multi Employees per "
"Session`, and add the allowed employees in the :guilabel:`Allowed Employees`"
" field."
